```python
def insert_after_character(string):
    return string.replace('a', 'an')

print(insert_after_character("banana"))          # returns "bannana"
print(insert_after_character("apple"))           # returns "anapple"
print(insert_after_character("abanana"))         # returns "abanannana"
print(insert_after_character("racecar"))         # returns "racecar"
print(insert_after_character(""))                # returns ""
```
